Selena Gomez appears to be cooking new music because the songstress was spotted outside a studio. The “Come And Get It” hitmaker was seen leaving a recording studio in Los Angeles on Tuesday night and this news is exciting for her fans. Considering the last time Gomez released a solo album is over three years ago, fans are hoping she was making new music at the studio. She hasn’t been totally absent from the airwaves as she has been featured here and there in some songs. Selena Gomez spotted outside a music studio | Photo – TMZ It would be recalled that Gomez received mental health treatment last year after having an emotional breakdown. She also had a major surgery in 2017 for a kidney transplant.